  89,23,"E oon √±alawma jahannama addee hombo wa…ói 70000 ujunere ginol, kala heen gootol na e mum 70000 wuluure malayka na ndasa mbo, ndeen noon aade siftoro ko o welsandino, kono ko siftorde nafata oon √±alawma, o √±alngu ko mbo njo…ìdi wonah mbo golle."
  89,24,"O wi*a sabu sattude nimsa: Haaniino mi ardina golle lobbe wonande nguurndam am ka laakara, ko …óaam woni goongo."
